data.description: Whether you are looking for your first home or a well-established property, this home has everything you are looking for. This two story home has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathroom has over 1, 811 square feet of cozy living space. Upon entry, you are greeted with warm colored flooring, high ceiling and huge bay window. A half bath on the main floor of the house for guest. Laundry room is also located downstairs. Entering the spacious eat-in kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter-top space and stainless steel appliances. In addition, this home offers plenty of natural lighting from the kitchen window, dining area, and rear glass door. Also on the main level, is the primary retreat where you will discover the primary bathroom that has a soaker tub, separate stand in shower and double his and her vanity sink and large walk in closet. On the second level is a loft area with overlook of the first floor living area. All roomy secondary bedrooms are upstairs with carpet and closets. A full secondary bath for the kids and overnight guest. The exterior features include brick, stone/rock front and gorgeous landscaping throughout the front of the house. Enjoy summer nights and weekends grilling or just lounging around on the deck and fenced in back yard. So hesitate no longer and schedule your viewing today, you won't be disappointed.
